We recommend that Management to:

a. 	Require the GSO and the Disposal Committee to conduct physical verification of unserviceable PPE,  to determine the present condition and mode of disposal;

b. 	Require the Disposal Committee to appraise the unserviceable PPE to be disposed through public auction;

c. 	Require the Disposal Committee to file an application for disposal with appropriate documents to the COA;

d. 	Require the Municipal Accountant to prepare the necessary adjusting journal entry to derecognize the PPE transferred and sold in the books of account; and

